  "title": "safety manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversee and implement all\n     workplace safety and health protocols at construction sites in Singapore.</li><li>Conduct regular safety audits\n     and inspections to ensure a safe working environment.</li><li>Ensure full compliance with\n     local regulations, including Singapore’s Workplace Safety and Health (WSH)\n     requirements.</li><li>Develop risk assessments and\n     safety management plans for ongoing projects.</li><li>Lead and deliver safety\n     training sessions for site personnel.</li><li>Investigate workplace incidents\n     and recommend corrective actions.</li><li>Maintain accurate documentation\n     and records related to safety and health matters.</li></ul>",
